high_descs: Walk towards the middle of the table on your left and turn left to face the lettuce on the table.
Pick up the lettuce from the table.
Turn left, walk towards the edge of the table, and then turn right towards the fridge and then turn left towards the sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Turn around and head towards the table.
Place the lettuce in between the fork and salt shaker on the table.
anns.task_desc: Wash the lettuce on the table.

high_descs: Face the center island in the middle.
Pick up the lettuce from the island.
Bring the lettuce to the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Bring the lettuce to the other side of the island.
Put the lettuce on the island next to the fork.
anns.task_desc: Clean the lettuce from the island, put it back on the island.

high_descs: turn to face the kitchen island
grab lettuce off of the kitchen island
move to the sink in the kitchen
place the lettuce in the kitchen sink and rinse it off, then pick it back up
walk over to the kitchen island again
place the clean lettuce down on the kitchen island
anns.task_desc: place clean lettuce down on the kitchen island
